{
  "stem": "17761.5",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We didn't know what happened to them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We didn't know how to get together.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They-- you don't have anything there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Didn't have any documents, no nothing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And at the given station, they probably arranged it by phone that these two wagons were detached at a given station.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And the-- the chief of the station, the commander of the station, told them, take this train.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "It goes in the same direction.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "But this train didn't stop at that station, so they went to another station.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And so they ended up in the front.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And they were caught-- these two Jews with beards-- on the front.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "They were brought to a commander, to [INAUDIBLE], a Russian commander, and he was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "He knew he-- he knew immediately they are not the great spies, these two guys.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "[LAUGHTER]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he gave them an escort, and they were brought back to the station where the wagons were, and when they-- they-- we were preparing to move back, we saw them coming.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we yelled to them, come, come.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They started to run.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We managed to bring them up into the wagons, and we went back to Czernowitz.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Where did you go from there?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To Czer-- in Czernowitz.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So in Czernowitz, we tried to find our way back to Vatra Dornei, to our home.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the Russians, they didn't let us do this.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "At the given moment, we got word from the [NON-ENGLISH] that we are allowed to introduce a petition to Stalin.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But this petition couldn't be signed only by members of the same family, because you are not allowed to organize yourselves.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So every family fills out a form, and we send it to Stalin.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it took a few months.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
